Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I'm on Page 02 of Thoracic MRI
Then 'Indication' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Mass' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Chest wall' radio button is enabled
And 'Mediastinal' radio button is enabled
And 'Intrapulmonary' radio button is enabled
And 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Infection' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Interstitial lung disease' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Pulmonary artery embolism' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Pulmonary hypertension' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Pneumothorax' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Cystic fibrosis' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Arthralgia' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Sternoclavicular joint' checkbox is enabled
And 'Follow-up' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Sternoclavicular joint' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
